import React from "react"

const Additem = () => {
  return (
    <form className="addForm" >
        <label htmlFor="addItem">Addlist</label>
          <input
          autoFocus
          id="addItem"
          type="text"
          placeholder="add item"
          required
          />
          <button
          type="submit"
          aria-label="Add item">
          </button>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Additem
